Strategy_resp: I imagined myself in the garage. I then let my mind wander from one item to another item that may be relevant.
I just let things come into my mind. I tried to relate each to another when possible.
I thought about sports that typically come on TV and then thought about sports in the Olympics.
I added a letter to the letter 'a' and tried to think of words that began with those two letters, then I'd add a different letter to 'a' and so on.
I just pictured my bedroom and bedrooms that I have been in, and tried to name things I recalled.
I added a second letter to 's' and tried to think of words that started with 's' plus another letter.
I tried to think of animals in different categories. Pets, jungle animals, sea animals, etc.
I just let words come to me. Tried combinations of letters to come up with words.
I looked around my kitchen since I'm currently in it on my computer.
